default.4.3
default              
defaultIT systems can prevent easy access and flow of information
default. 
defaultFor example, one Co-creating Health team faced the problem of GPs using different IT systems, which prevented them from flagging patients participating in the 
defaulttraining 
defaultprogramme. 
