default&#xa0;default5default.0default              defaultWhat we have learneddefault about how to overcome these barriersdefault&#xa0;default5
default.1
default              
defaultCreating a culture that supports person-centred care is a significant challenge
default. 
defaultOur programme teams 
defaulthave 
defaulthad to be creative and
default flexible to overcome barriers.
default Support from senior leadership – up to trust board levels –
default has been vital in 
defaultgaining traction.
